                  <h2 style="color: #2f77b0; font-size: 8pt;">ELIGIBILITY</h2>
                  <p style="font-size: 6pt;   line-height: 12px;">
                    Any natural person who applies for this Scheme and hereafter referred as life proposed, to whom the Policyholder has agreed in principle to grant a loan, must give his written consent thereto and by filling in, dating and signing an appropriate membership application form which will be remitted to him by ABSA Bank (Mauritius) Ltd. The insurer shall issue confirmation of acceptance only after the life proposed has satisfied the NICL underwriting requirements. In the event where terms are being restricted or extra premium being charged, the written consent and payment of the extra premium must be received by the Insurer prior to beginning of coverage.
                  </p>
                  <h2 style="color: #2f77b0; font-size: 8pt;">EFFECTIVE DATE</h2>
                  <p style="font-size: 6pt;   line-height: 12px;">
                    The insurance cover shall take effect on the date the loan credit facility is disbursed and the Life Assured has satisfied the insurer underwriting requirements.
                  </p>
                </td>
