                  <h2 style="color: #2f77b0; font-size: 8pt;">CONFIDENTIALITY</h2>
                  <p style="font-size: 6pt;   line-height: 12px;">
                    Your personal data shall be processed as per the applicable laws pertaining to Data Protection. By signing the insurance application form or any other related questionnaires you agree that your personal information may be disclosed in strictest confidence by the insurer for evaluation of coverage eligibility and claim assessment and that the Life Assured is agreeable to that.
                  </p>
                  <h2 style="color: #2f77b0; font-size: 8pt;">COMMISSION</h2>
                  <p style="font-size: 6pt;   line-height: 12px;">
                    A commission of 15% of basic premium is payable to ABSA throughout the term of the cover.
                  </p>
                  <h2 style="color: #2f77b0; font-size: 8pt;">TERMINATION OF COVER</h2>
                  <p style="font-size: 6pt;  line-height: 12px; margin-bottom: 0;">
                    The assurance cover will cease and no benefits will become payable on:
                  </p>
                  <ul style="margin-left: 0; padding-left: 10px;">
                    <li style="font-size: 6pt;   line-height: 12px;">Life Assured attained 70 years</li>
                    <li style="font-size: 6pt;   line-height: 12px;">cessation of premium payment to the insurer</li>
                    <li style="font-size: 6pt;   line-height: 12px;">full settlement of loan contracted;</li>
                    <li style="font-size: 6pt;   line-height: 12px;">the benefit in respect of the Life Assured is paid-out.</li>
                  </ul>
                  <h2 style="color: #2f77b0; font-size: 8pt;">SUM ASSURED</h2>
                  <p style="font-size: 6pt;   line-height: 12px;">
                    In the event the Life Assured dies or becomes totally and permanently disabled prior to the expiry of the term of cover, the outstanding loan amount of the Life Assured shall be paid off to ABSA Bank (Mauritius) Ltd by NICL. The death or total and permanent disability proceeds occurring during the cover period, shall not exceed the outstanding capital amount of the credit.
                  </p>
                  <h2 style="color: #2f77b0; font-size: 8pt;">RISKS COVERED AND EXCLUSIONS</h2>
                  <ul style="list-style: none; margin-left: 0;padding-left: 0;">
                    <li>
                      <h3 style="color: #2f77b0; font-size: 6pt;  line-height: 12px; margin-bottom: 0;">(1) Death</h3>
                      <p style="font-size: 6pt;  line-height: 12px; margin-top: 0;">Death arising as a result of natural or accidental cause is covered except if it is caused due to suicide within 12 months from date of commencement of the risk.</p>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                      <h3 style="color: #2f77b0; font-size: 6pt;  line-height: 12px; margin-bottom: 0;">(2) Total and Permanent Disability</h3>
                      <p style="font-size: 6pt;  line-height: 12px; margin-top: 0;">It refers to the total and permanent inability of the Life Assured as a result of accident, injury and illness to:</p>
                      <ul style="padding-left: 10px;">
                        <li style="font-size: 6pt;  line-height: 12px; list-style-type: disc;">
                          Engage in his own or similar occupation for which he is suited by experience, training or education; or
                        </li>
                      </ul>
                    </li>
                  </ul>

                </td>
