                    </li>
                  </ul>
                  <p style="font-size: 6pt;  line-height: 12px; margin-top: 0;">
                    The disability benefit does not apply in the event of the disability being, directly or indirectly caused as a result of:
                  </p>
                  <ul style="list-style: none; padding-left: 0;">
                    <li style="font-size: 6pt;   line-height: 12px;">
                      a) Self-Inflicted Injury;
                    </li>
                    <li style="font-size: 6pt;   line-height: 12px;">
                      b) Under the influence of alcohol;
                    </li>
                    <li style="font-size: 6pt;   line-height: 12px;">
